        {
            "title": "滬深A股早市持續回升 深指跑贏半日升1.3% 芯片板塊再受青睞",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市今早延續昨午拗腰倒升的動力，滬深兩市股指早市全程報升，芯片板塊價量齊升，華虹(01347)A股(688347.SH)更現雙位數升幅。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"華虹半導體官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"華虹半導體官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">華虹半導體官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早輕微高開6點後一直反覆向好，最高曾見3946點，升23點，半日低位3928點時也升6點；滬指中午收報3938點，仍漲16點或0.42%，半日成交5247.87億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指昨天收復萬三點關後，今早再新跑贏，甫開市即升65點報13091點見半日低位，尾市最高衝上13215點，漲190點；深指中午收報13195點，升169點或1.3%，成交7032.35億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也升30點或0.66%，收報4636點；創業板指數升63點或2.09%，報3126點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寒武紀官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250311_FI_source-web_688256-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寒武紀官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250311_FI_source-web_688256-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寒武紀官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">主要芯片股均價量齊升，華虹A股中午收報125.59元，飆13.27%，成交46.11億元。寒武紀(688256.SH)與中芯國際(00981)A股(688981.SH)成交穩佔滬A股首兩位，寒武紀半日升3.58%，報1448.93元，交投96.05億元；中芯A股升3.28%，報132.51元，交投也有79.37億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15367469-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1a%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e6%8c%81%e7%ba%8c%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%87-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%91%e8%b4%8f%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%8d%871-3-%e8%8a%af%e7%89%87%e6%9d%bf%e5%a1%8a%e5%86%8d",
